trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Form"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Form"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: FormCollection is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application> object to list the currently open forms in an application through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.OpenForms%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: FormCollection brukes av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application>objektet til å vise skjemaene som er åpen i et program ved hjelp av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.OpenForms%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.OpenForms%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.FormCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.FormCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets an element in the collection by its numeric index.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et element i samlingen av den numeriske indeksen.

trans-unit.source: The location of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Form"></xref> within the collection.
trans-unit.target: Plasseringen av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Form"> </xref> i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The form at the specified index.
Gets or sets an element in the collection by the name of the associated <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Form"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et element i samlingen av navnet på den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Form"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The form with the specified name.
